"1","name":"Description","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"1","source_data":{"description":"<p>Layer the virus suspension onto 100-400 mg\/mL (10-40%) linear sucrose gradients equilibriated with 50 mM Tris-HCl made in polypropylene\u00a0tubes (layer approximately 3-4 mL per gradient).<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>*To make sucrose stocks, add 10-40% sucrose to Tris-HCl and autoclave.<\/p>"},"is_project":0}]},{"id":"219548","is_changed":"0","original_id":"0","is_skipped":"0","is_checked":"0","guid":"63433B236F164B958C9D6C6AE51E9F93","previous_guid":"E5B9313C372B410EB21FFD1B90BBD193","previous_id":"219395","last_modified":"1502719008","components":[{"component_id":"989278","previous_id":0,"original_id":"0","guid":"543266B917CF4A289B4179B9711FCF86","previous_guid":null,"component_type_id":"6","data_id":null,"data":null,"order_id":"0","name":"Section","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"6","source_data":{"section":null},"is_project":0},{"component_id":"284067","previous_id":"989278","original_id":"0","guid":"09FCE0C9B66D4A5BB2765C65898A47D6","previous_guid":"543266B917CF4A289B4179B9711FCF86","component_type_id":"1","data_id":"0","data":"<p>Centrifuge the gradients in the ultracentrifuge\u00a0at 20,000 rpm, 20 min, 4\u00baC. The virus will be the major band about 1\/2 to 2\/3 deep in the gradient.<\/p>","order_id":"1","name":"Description","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"1","source_data":{"description":"<p>Centrifuge the gradients in the ultracentrifuge\u00a0at 20,000 rpm, 20 min, 4\u00baC. The virus will be the major band about 1\/2 to 2\/3 deep in the gradient.<\/p>"},"is_project":0}]},{"id":"219631","is_changed":"0","original_id":"0","is_skipped":"0","is_checked":"0","guid":"E66D5334D10640FBAA496FAE2A068253","previous_guid":"63433B236F164B958C9D6C6AE51E9F93","previous_id":"219548","last_modified":"1502719008","components":[{"component_id":"989279","previous_id":0,"original_id":"0","guid":"81219475E8E7463182D2FDD749A9C708","previous_guid":null,"component_type_id":"6","data_id":null,"data":nul